585
00:25:08,280 --> 00:25:09,190
Get out of here.

586
00:25:10,140 --> 00:25:11,560
Yes, get out.

587
00:25:11,700 --> 00:25:12,780
Be quick!

588
00:25:12,800 --> 00:25:13,530
Go away!

589
00:25:13,560 --> 00:25:15,100
Go away!

590
00:25:15,310 --> 00:25:15,950
